content:
Manage Group Benefits Census Members and Dependents

You can manage census members and dependents with the Vlocity Insurance Census Lightning web component.

Add a Group Benefits Census Member: Add a member to a census right from the Vlocity Insurance Census Lightning web component.

Add a Dependent to a Group Benefits Census Member: Add a dependent for a member to a census right from the Vlocity Insurance Census Lightning web component.

Delete a Member or Dependent: Delete a member or dependent by clicking the delete button, then rerating the quote.

Update a Group Benefits Census Member or Dependent: Update a member or dependent record right from the Vlocity Insurance Census Lightning web component.
title: Managing Insurance Group Benefits Census
